    {
      "id": "69eb54e80000000000f51b4c",
      "text": "[https://kotobank.jp/word/%E3%82%AE%E3%82%A2-472064 ギアとは？ 意味や使い方 - コトバンク]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777030377,
      "updated": 1777030377
    },
    {
      "id": "6674f29e5b98c20000076e84",
      "text": ">１ 歯車。とくに、互いにかみ合う歯車のうち、歯数の多いほう。→[ピニオン]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1718940318,
      "updated": 1777030483
    },
    {
      "id": "6674f2b95b98c20000076e85",
      "text": ">２ 歯車を組み合わせた動力伝動装置。ギヤ。「変速ギア」",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1718940346,
      "updated": 1777030483
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb61c80000000000482797",
      "text": " [デフギア]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777033672,
      "updated": 1777033700
    },
    {
      "id": "6674f2b95b98c20000076e86",
      "text": ">３ 道具。用具一式。「キャンプギア」",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1718940346,
      "updated": 1777030483
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb54e60000000000f51b48",
      "text": " [my new gear...]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777030374,
      "updated": 1777030483
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb54ff0000000000f51b4d",
      "text": "  新しい機材を購入したときに自慢してツイートするときに使う",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777030399,
      "updated": 1777030483
    },
    {
      "id": "6674f29b5b98c20000076e83",
      "text": " [ヘッドギア]",
